http://www.savers.org:80/heritage/library/categories/forpol/fyi95.html 204.71.237.73 19970108154459 text/html 16834
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 15:45:02 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 17-Apr-96 15:05:21 GMT
