<li>Terry L. Anderson and Donald R. Leal, <I>Free Market Environmentalism</I>, Pacific Research Institute for Public Policy Research, 1991, p. 112, citing Ed Zern, "By Yon Bonny Banks," Field and Stream, Vol. 86 (September 1981), p. 120.<p>
