Shanahan, John, "The Conservative As Environmentalist," <i>Heritage Lecture</i> No. 358, November 19, 1991.
<p>
Shanahan, John and Thierer, Adam, "Can We Save Even More Lives?: Understanding the 'Opportunity Costs' of Regulation," <i>F.Y.I.</i> No. 11, February 28, 1994.
<P>       
